            "content": [
              {
                "nodeType": "text",
                "value": "Mass Combat",
                "marks": [],
                "data": {}
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "nodeType": "paragraph",
            "data": {},
            "content": [
              {
                "nodeType": "text",
                "value": "At higher levels, characters could fight hordes or armies of enemies. The game master can group creatures that are significantly lower level than the characters into units. When creating a unit, use the statistics of the creature as normal except modify the statistics as shown on the below table.",
                "marks": [],
                "data": {}
