          {
            "nodeType": "paragraph",
            "data": {},
            "content": [
              {
                "nodeType": "text",
                "value": "When charging, gain advantage on the attack and gain an extra damage dice. Cavalry units may leave combat without drawing opportunity attacks. When being attacked by units with a polearm gain disadvantage to the defense agility roll. This requires the unit be mounted on some form of cavalry such as horses (for humans) or something similar such as spiders (for goblins).",
                "marks": [],
                "data": {}
